Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:06.13,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Romalia has already
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.98,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,dispatched a fleet to counter ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.98,0:00:11.01,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The stage will soon be set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:12.85,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:15.96,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly be \Nplanning to declare war?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:16.79,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,War?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.80,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wars are started by those \Nwho wish for gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:24.04,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I wish for nothing. I just want to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:27.34,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the preparations, Sheffield.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.05,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.34,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:42.64,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, I'm a Familiar of the Void.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.76,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Myozunitonirun, the Mind of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.68,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only one capable \Nof releasing the power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.43,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,locked within the Founder's Round Mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:55.21,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Those runes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:57.76,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,When I use this mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:01:02.94,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,I can transfer a Void \NMage's power to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.55,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I needed your destruction \Nspell, Explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.88,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,so that I may use these
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.96,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,fire stones at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:58.02,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(570,1)}The Incompetent King Gone Mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.15,CRZero,Officer,0000,0000,0000,,The Gallian fleet has stopped \N1200 meters from our border.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.70,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that distance and set \Nup a defensive perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.30,CRZero,Officer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.24,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,What are you plotting now, Joseph?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.60,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.68,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,It's no small thing, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.79,0:03:34.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess you're over there, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:38.33,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening, Your Holiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.36,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,This is most likely one \Nof Joseph's feints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.78,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to make sure the Void Mages,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.44,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,besides him, do not get any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.74,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he will \Nmake an actual attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.44,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.21,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But then, why did he take Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.61,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Aeor suhn fil jarnsaks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.46,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,os suhn uriu rad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:08.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you using my spells for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:11.73,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Stick around and you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:19.10,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Beozus yul sviel kan oshel,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:22.21,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,jer isa undun hagal,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.64,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,beocun ir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.31,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.17,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.22,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Unexpectedly, I feel nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.68,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Ready the next fire stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.26,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's destroying his own men, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:08.09,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha! Please, let me ride Sylphid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.60,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:24.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Julio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.71,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of stopping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:30.75,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I wanted to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.22,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,R-Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.89,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.63,CRZero,Captain,0000,0000,0000,,Come about 180 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.28,CRZero,Man,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:51.11,CRZero,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:52.73,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.45,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But it's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:07.94,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.09,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:12.93,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Saito and Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.53,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha's gone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.51,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:18.22,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.89,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,What's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.83,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,A gargoyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.49,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.12,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to get the \Ntownspeople to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What is your objective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.59,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Objective?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.00,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,My objective is death and destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.18,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.37,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out what level
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:04.10,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,of cruelty will actually \Nmake me feel remorse,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.67,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and if I am capable of \Nshedding tears, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.97,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that, you'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.41,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.91,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,...for someone like me, who had to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.44,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,his emotions as he grew up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:16.25,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,shadow of a superior younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.93,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother, Charles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.72,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.22,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But when your gift for \Nmagic was awakened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.06,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,everything changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:32.25,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, my soul has \Nonly thirsted for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.60,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what riches I amassed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.28,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many people I killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.34,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I could find no peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.48,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Charles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.37,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think destroying a city
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:47.28,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,can make my heart start beating again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:51.52,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.14,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:03.70,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.30,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.27,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it back at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.86,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, Saito, Saito, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:32.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, Saito, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:37.73,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, Saito, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:44.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to stop the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.70,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,I've retrieved the fire stone \N safe and sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.48,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,but it appears the girl's life is forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.32,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it will be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:07.89,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:17.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So that's Joseph, King of Gallia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:20.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I guess all I have to do \Nis keep him from casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.01,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,It's been too long, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.42,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get in my master's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.64,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop that explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.76,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please remain calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.49,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Please take shelter in the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.20,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really all right for us to use
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.95,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,the cathedral as an evacuation shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:03.22,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.19,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I will personally take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.23,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,for those useless priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.37,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I nailed that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.16,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche... Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:19.24,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your swift decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.57,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us lead everyone \Ninto the cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.29,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.18,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tabitha and Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.35,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Air Cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:40.94,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.99,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they're \Nchasing the gargoyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:50.09,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,The gargoyles caused that \Nexplosion a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.50,CRZero,Colbert,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that one will do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:56.37,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are trying to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.12,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.12,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pal, this is never going to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The gargoyles get their \Npower from Myozunitonirun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't get anywhere, \Nuntil I can get some hits on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:36.13,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is one of those "out of place relics"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.23,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that are kept in Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.07,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make good use of it, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.12,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.06,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to fight you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.98,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,They're having a hard time of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:15.78,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.48,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,knowing that I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.66,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Westwood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.21,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}is{\i0} something you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.00,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there that time when you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.86,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,made everyone forget all \Nthose things with magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.39,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.19,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.13,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Naucid is eywath,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.47,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,hagraz yul beog,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.21,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,nied ees algihz,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.61,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,berkana man ragu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.40,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.03,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Joseph's ship. \NYou should get off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:10.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be at Saito's side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.51,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:23.00,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Beozus yul sviel kan oshel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:26.91,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Stop casting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.43,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.56,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be blowing up anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.37,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect the \Ncity and everyone in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.16,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.17,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much honesty in \Nyour eyes, it's almost blinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.40,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I was like you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.56,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose there's no going back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.15,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is useless against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.91,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Void Magic \Nthat was bestowed upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:13:59.88,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.78,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose did God \Ngrant me this spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:09.23,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if he's urging me to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.17,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:15.35,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I must be getting back \Nto the task at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:21.91,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Pal, if he gets you with \Nthat, you're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.22,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Pal...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:32.17,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,In my world, we have an \Nexpression, "the mind's eye."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:36.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use that to track \Nyour movements, Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.32,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:52.09,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this the great "mind's eye"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:04.48,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to be Gandalfr \Nto learn how to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.28,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think is faster, \Nyour sword, or mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.31,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Windy Icicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:31.88,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:33.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten worse from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:43.99,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.16,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I see you inherited your \Nfather's magic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.46,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,You killed my father and you \Nbroke my mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.80,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:57.90,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,As you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.26,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Then do with me as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.77,CRZero,Joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That is your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha, you shouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to \Nhave his blood on your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:11.42,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:13.05,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.39,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you've got to stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.20,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This is her decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:21.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:24.13,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she sullies her hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,she has to decide this for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:26.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.84,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who has to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'll respect your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:48.02,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hand him over to Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you're treated right away, you'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:56.02,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Live, and atone for your sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:01.86,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.42,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow King Joseph to be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.87,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,subjected to something so degrading!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:06.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.47,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.02,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,The incantation was almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:14.65,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,From here, even my own power \Nis enough to make it explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:22.70,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,My lord's life is rapidly fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.42,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,Please, leave me alone with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We had them cornered, and \Nthen we let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:40.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:42.64,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:18:00.49,CRZero,Sheffield,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't kissed since \Nthe contract, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm returning this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.66,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,For your actions, I'd like to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.49,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,thank you from the bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.54,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:40.74,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Tabitha,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:44.80,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,and you, Saito Chevalier de Hiraga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:48.58,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,How are your wounds, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.71,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Great, thanks to your \Nhealing magic, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.21,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:58.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Julio, that pistol you \Ngave me came in handy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:18:59.72,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,Did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.72,CRZero,Julio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:03.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave me that because you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.69,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,wanted me to defeat Joseph, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but think,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,you make Louise into a shrine maiden,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,she gets kidnapped by Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I go to save her, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.27,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I take Joseph down in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Seemed like everything
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,was going right according to your plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! How can you say such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:29.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong, Your Holiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.21,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.34,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I can't deny it outright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.94,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,We made a Void Mage \Ninto a shrine maiden,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.75,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,not to convince him, but to provoke him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.23,0:19:43.53,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,We expected Joseph to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:45.40,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,No, we hoped he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.23,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,If that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:51.73,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,we would have a reason to \Nlaunch a holy war against Gallia
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:55.22,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,and get rid of Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.72,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,But you must believe me when
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:59.41,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I say that it was never our intention
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:03.59,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,to put Miss Vallière in \Nsuch a dangerous position.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:08.75,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,Nor did we expect Joseph to \Ncause so much destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:10.02,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,I hope
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.28,CRZero,Vittorio,0000,0000,0000,,you can forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:19.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:21.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you should \Nsay something to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If King Joseph is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:26.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,then another Void Mage will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:29.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure, then, it'll be easy for \Nthe four of us to join forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that makes it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:34.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You were almost killed in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:36.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But you were there to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:41.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I knew back then that you would
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:43.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,definitely be coming soon to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:49.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It was like I could see \Nyou waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I know you'll always be \Nthere to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.58,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:56.86,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,They're all waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:03.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:09.12,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a strong bond they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:12.69,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could I ever think
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:14.53,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Saito might be my familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:17.35,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:25.33,CRZero,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's the saint of Aquileia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.00,CRZero,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,And the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.55,CRZero,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This is so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:32.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.00,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is praising \Nthe saint of Aquileia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.38,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,and the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:41.08,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the saint of Aquileia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.52,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:47.05,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the saint of Aquileia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:49.65,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:53.04,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the saint of Aquileia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:29.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You lecherous dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:31.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you saved \NRomalia doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will let it slide that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.43,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,you're drooling over other women!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:37.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Queen's Reward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:41.05,Next-Ep-Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(270,1}The Queen's Reward
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:40.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,After this, let's look for a \Ncastle just for the two of us.
